<plot>Oubliette is a short film about a young man and his girlfriend about to engage in their first sexual encounter. After talking about where their future is going they decide to culminate their relationship and secure their love for each other in way 'only lovers can.' Between a meddling father and the feeling of loss for the young mans mother the couple decide that the only strength they truly have is their love for each other. But is everything as it seems?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?417378</url></doc>
